Privacy Policy – HaxBall Avatar + Spam + Custom Keys

Last updated: June 20, 2026

This browser extension ("Extension") works only on the haxball.com domain and improves user experience by storing the following settings locally on your device:

Key bindings (Avatar Toggle, Spam Toggle, Hit/Spam Key)
Default avatar emoji
Panel display preference (collapsed / expanded view)

This data is stored in your browser’s local storage (localStorage / chrome.storage) and remains only on your device.

Data we do NOT collect:

This Extension does not collect, store, or transmit any of the following:

Name, email, location, IP address, browsing history, financial information, identity data, health data, or personal communications
Any user activity tracking (keystrokes, mouse movements, click tracking, etc.)
Data sharing:

The Extension does not send any data to external servers, does not share data with third parties, and does not sell any information. No data is transmitted over the internet.

Remote code:

The Extension contains all its code within its own package. It does not download or execute any external scripts at runtime.

